gomodel:SYNGO_17  a       owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Discrete labeling is visualised along membranes of both parallel fiber terminals and typical thin intervaricose segments of parallel fiber axons\n\n5/12/2016 Pim\n- Literal Fig 2; \"Discrete labeling is visualized along the membranes of both parallel fiber terminals (small arrows in a and e) and typical thin intervaricose segments of parallel fiber axons (ax in a , c - f). Note that active zones are devoid of silver particles (arrowheads in a - e). \"\n- integral component in the annotation is derived from TM-domains in the annotated protein.. Experimental description: Figure 2: \"Ultrastructural localization of Kv3.3 in the **rat** cerebellar molecular layer using the pre-embedding immunogold method.\"" , "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0099056 replaced by GO:0042734" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-9425-2935" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2514-0216" ;
        dc:date           "2024-03-14" ;
